sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant O as Order service
    participant S as Chronicle
    participant W as Notify worker
    W->>S: PUT __ds/subscriptions/receipts (webhook, pattern orders/**)
    S-->>W: 201 Created — signing kid ds_abc123
    O->>S: POST orders/A1234 "paid"
    S-->>O: 204 — durably appended
    Note over S: append matches · bump generation · arm lease
    S->>W: POST /hooks — signed wake (orders/A1234 behind)
    Note over W: verify Ed25519 sig · send the receipt email
    W-->>S: 200 done:true
    Note over S: auto-ack · cursor advances · back to idle
    O->>S: POST orders/A1234 "shipped"
    S->>W: POST /hooks — signed wake
    W-->>S: 503 — receiver down
    Note over S: schedule retry · backoff 1s to 60s · persisted
    S->>W: POST /hooks — retry after backoff
    W-->>S: 200 done:true
